Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.32,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月1日礼拜一4点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是插入吧主播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天起会变冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.16,0:00:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你有计划吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.00,0:00:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在家里上网 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.08,0:00:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在家里给人干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.64,0:00:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去兜风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜风真好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.92,0:01:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.88,0:01:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊在大自然包围下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.16,0:01:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈地被干 真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在户外吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.76,0:01:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,户外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好耶 大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.92,0:01:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊在那里干啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.52,0:01:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是播报新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.24,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位这边请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.16,0:02:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着啊 要播报这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希崎 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.24,0:02:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认真一点不行 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.72,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且叫你要一直笑脸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还害羞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 插入吧是健康的节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.40,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样没有人看喔 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好加油吧 一定要创收视率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5秒前432
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了舒压按摩时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.16,0:03:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天啊来到目前效果拔群的话题按摩店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.72,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我要好好体验精油按师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.64,0:03:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.51,0:03:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是田中也不是中岛是小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.24,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊想挖鼻孔 是吗拍歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.56,0:04:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作身体很疲劳 尤其是脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是会硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在意的吗 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时会很紧张会流汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有停止流汗的方法 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.52,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那马上开始...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.36,0:05:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么马上 可以吗 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了 那么体验店里的人气秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好感受吧
