Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔
